<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>sva</unclear>sti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē lōkaratnāvaniśaśigaṇitē
<lb n="2"/>vriścikaṁ yāti bhānau śuklē kaṁddarppatithyā(ṁ) mmu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dusalisacivā bhānudēvābhivridyai <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> konnagrāmē
<lb n="4"/>pradadyā tkamaṭhapurapatē<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> bradhnavāṭē pramāṇaṁ
<lb n="5"/>bhūbhāgaṁ tacca paṁccāmritamaṇisamayē yennivē
<lb n="6" break="no"/>dyaṁ tadutthaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tāṁbūladvayasaṁyutaṁ pariryyalaṁ ccha
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kaṁ cca sāpūpakaṁ niṣkaikēna savanvitaṁ bhagavata<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrī
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kāryyasaṁsiddhayē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> viprēbhyō viracayya paṁccadaśa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>saṁkhyā nāyakāsyabhyadādājñāmāpya munīśvarō naraha
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ri<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrībhānudēvaśrituḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> brāhmaṇanāmāni likhyaṁttē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="11"/>kauṁḍḍinyagōtrē kommanasōmayājinaḥ bhāradvājagōtrē
<lb n="12"/>nāmupuḍiyaśāsi yejñēśvarappanakūrmmanāthapaṭṭapēru
<lb n="13" break="no"/>māṁḍidāsimēruAppananāmānaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kāśyapagōtrē
<lb n="14"/>śrīkri<unclear>ṣṇa</unclear>dāsitiruveṁgaḷadāsi<supplied reason="omitted">nā</supplied>mānau <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kauṁḍinyagō
<lb n="15" break="no"/>trē kaṟṟipurāyināyakātallemaṁccinamānau <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> hari
<lb n="16" break="no"/>tagōtrē kū<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>mmanāthaśarmma vatsagōtrē Annēśarmma
<lb n="17" break="no"/>kāśyapagōtrē sthānāpatirēkaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="18"/>kapigōtrē sūryyadēvabhaṭṭōpādhyāyāḥ ppu
<lb n="19" break="no"/>rāṇapāṭhakāḥ pūtimāṣagōtrē śāṣanādhi
<lb n="20" break="no"/>kārī kāmadēva sēnādhīśvarāḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ētē vīraśrībhānu
<lb n="21" break="no"/>dēvājñayā narāhariśrīcaraṇapratiṣṭitā paṁccada 
<lb n="22" break="no"/>śa vaiṣṇavanāyakā Aparē triṁśannāyakāśca paṁcō
<lb n="23" break="no"/>ttaracatvāriṁśat brāhmaṇā sarvvaissammīḷya sakala
<lb n="24" break="no"/>śrīkāryyāṇi nirvvatyācaṁdrārkkaṁ sukhamanubhavaṁttu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="25"/>svadattāṁ paradattāṁ vā yō harētu vasuṁdharāṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> ṣaṣṭiṁ
<lb n="26"/>varuṣasahasrāṇi viṣṭāyāṁ jā<supplied reason="omitted">ya</supplied>tē krimi[ḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>*]
<lb n="27"/>Uddhritya kudupigrāmaṁ pū<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>vvaluptaṁ munīśvaraḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> bhāṁ
<lb n="28" break="no"/>ḍāgārē tu yeddēyamēbhistasyādadātsvayaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

